1. mvn clean package
2. mvn clean package docker:build 	// to build a docker image.

Pre-requisite ->
	1. in maven (settings.xml) add the following entry under the <servers> tag
				<servers>
					<server>
					      <id>docker.io</id>
					      <username>some_user</username>
					      <password>some_user_password</password>
					    </server>
				</servers>
	2. in the project pom.xml make sure make sure the following tag has the image prefix of your account name i.e.
				<docker.image.prefix>some_user</docker.image.prefix>
		